title: President Donald J. Trump is Furthering America’s Enduring Partnership with Poland – The White House
content:
Fact Sheets			

		Foreign Policy	

Issued on:
June 12, 2019
Poland has chosen its place among the free and independent nations of the world and as a loyal ally and strategic partner of the United States.
						President Donald J. Trump					ESSENTIAL ALLIANCE AND FRIENDSHIP: Poland is an essential ally, an exemplary member of NATO, and has long been a friend of the United States.ROBUST SECURITY RELATIONSHIP: The United States and Poland are partners in the fight for freedom around the world.ENERGY AND ECONOMIC COOPERATION: The United States and Poland are committed to achieving energy diversity in Europe and enhancing economic development.
